GateDocument.TextWithNodes: Ericsson says wins 1.2 bln SKR China order . STOCKHOLM 1996-08-30 Swedish telecoms group LM Ericsson AB said on Friday it won an order worth 1.2 billion crowns for a fixed public telecoms network in the Guangdong province of China . Ericsson said in a statement the order was from the Guangdong Post and Telecommunications Administration ( GPTA ) . The order included AXE switching equipment , ISDN equipment , Intelligent Network ( IN ) products , broad-band multi-media communication network products , services and training , Ericsson spokesman Per Zetterquist told Reuters . Deliveries are due to be completed by 1999 , the company said . -- Stockholm newsroom +46-8-700 1017
